15. Qxb7 Rb8 16. Qxa7 Rxb3 {with more than enough compensation.}) 15. Bxe4 fxe4
16. Kd2 g5 17. b4 Rc8 18. Rac1 Bb8 19. a4 Qxb5 20. Nxb5 Rxc1 21. Rxc1 Kd7 {
