both sides of the board. Eventually White will not be able to defend
everything.} 25. Rb1 Bg4 26. b5 Bxe2 27. Kxe2 Bxg3 $19 28. b6 a6 29. Rc1 Bd6
30. Nc3 Ke6 31. a5 g4 32. Na4 g3 33. Nc5+ Bxc5 34. dxc5 Kd7 35. c6+ bxc6 36. b7
Rxf2+ 37. Ke1 Rb2 0-1

