1. d4 Nf6 2. Bg5 d5 3. Bxf6 exf6 4. e3 Bd6 5. Bd3 c6 $1 {When we see Bd3, we
POSTPONE castling!} 6. Qf3 ({What about} 6. Nd2 {? We can play} Nd7 $1 {
I like this move best, since it sets a small trap for White.} ({or} 6... f5 $1
7. Qf3 g6 8. h4 Nd7 9. h5 Nf6 10. hxg6 fxg6 $17) 7. Ne2 ({If White gets lured
into} 7. Qf3 $2 {then Black is already better after} g6 $15 8. g4 (8. Ne2 f5
$15) 8... h5 9. h3 Nf8 $17 {White cannot keep his structure on the kingside
intact.}) 7... O-O 8. O-O g6 9. c4 dxc4 10. Nxc4 Bc7 11. Qc2 f5 12. Rac1 Nf6
$11) 6... g6 $1 7. Nd2 ({If White prevents ...f5 with} 7. g4 {, we strike with}
h5 $1 8. h3 hxg4 (8... Nd7 $15) 9. hxg4 Rxh1 10. Qxh1 Bxg4 $17) 7... f5 $15 8.
O-O-O $2 Nd7 9. Ne2 Nf6 $17 {Black is much better - the rest of the game is
not so relevant!} 10. Nf4 O-O 11. c4 dxc4 12. Bxc4 Kg7 13. h4 h5 14. Kb1 Bd7
15. Ka1 Qe7 16. Rhe1 Rfe8 17. Qg3 b5 18. Bd3 Kh7 19. Nf3 Ne4 20. Bxe4 fxe4 21.
