42. Qe2 Qxe2 43. Rxe2 Rxd4 44. Rxd4 Rxd4 45. Bh3 Rd3 {0-1 (45) Mamedyarov,S 
(2764)-Vachier Lagrave,M (2778) Saint Louis 2019} 0-1

