Ne5 $6 Rc8 $15 11. Nxc6 $6 {White loses time.} Rxc6 $17 12. g4 $2 {White had a
difficult position in any case, but this allows a strong exchange sacrifice
after which his position can no longer be saved.} Rxc3 $1 13. bxc3 Qa5 (13...
