1. d4 Nf6 2. Nf3 e6 3. e3 b6 4. Bd3 Bb7 5. O-O g6 6. c4 Bg7 7. Nc3 O-O 8. e4 d6
9. h3 Nbd7 10. Bc2 e5 11. Re1 Re8 12. d5 a5 {Black will play ...Nc5, the
b7-bishop will later be rerouted via c8.} 13. a3 Rf8 {The rook was misplaced
on e8 - Black needs to prepare ...f5.} 14. Be3 h6 15. b4 Nh7 16. c5 {White
manages to play c5, but she has to exchange her dark-squared bishop.} axb4 17.
axb4 Rxa1 18. Qxa1 bxc5 19. bxc5 Nxc5 20. Bxc5 dxc5 21. Qa7 Bc8 22. Nb5 Ng5 {
We reached some unclear position with active counterplay for Black.} 23. Nxg5
Qxg5 24. Re3 Bxh3 25. Rxh3 Qc1+ 26. Kh2 Qxc2 27. f3 h5 28. Qxc7 Qb2 29. Qxc5
Bh6 30. Rh4 Bg5 0-1

