well placed to exploit the weak b6-square, while Black has an excellent knight
on d5. There is also the plan ...Bc6-b5.} 16. Rc1 (16. Qe2 Bc6 17. Rac1 Bb5)
16... Rb8 $15) 13. c4 bxc4 14. Nxc4 d5 $2 (14... Nd5 $2 {is longer possible
