1. d4 Nf6 2. Nf3 e6 3. Bf4 c5 4. e3 cxd4 5. exd4 Be7 6. c3 d6 7. Bd3 Nbd7 8.
Nbd2 b6 9. Qe2 Bb7 10. O-O O-O 11. h3 Re8 12. Bg3 a6 13. Ng5 Bf8 {Protecting
against possible sacrifices.} 14. Nde4 h6 15. Nf3 {White has achieved nothing
and Black facilitates favorable exchanges.} Nxe4 16. Bxe4 Bxe4 17. Qxe4 b5 {
Black already has a small advantage.} 18. Qe2 Nb6 19. Nd2 Qd7 20. Rfe1 Qc6 21.
Rac1 Rac8 22. Qg4 Qd5 23. b3 Rc6 24. Ne4 Kh8 25. Qf3 Qf5 26. Qe2 Rec8 27. Bh2
