play} a6 {Then a5 can be met with ...b5.}) 10... O-O 11. Ne4 {As we already
know from the analogous positions from the London System, exchanges favour
Black.} Nxe4 12. Bxe7 Qxe7 ({Sometimes} 12... Nxc3 $2 {is possible. Here it
does not work well:} 13. Bxd8 ({After} 13. Bxh7+ {Black survives with} Kh8 $1
