queenside, whereas White does not know what to do.} 15. Bxf6 (15. Re1 Ba6)
15... Bxf6 16. Qc5 (16. e4 d5 17. e5 Be7 $17) 16... Ba6 17. Qxa7 Bxe2 18. Rfc1
