1. d4 Nf6 2. Nf3 e6 3. g3 b5 4. Bg2 Bb7 5. O-O c5 6. Bg5 Na6 $2 {This move is
a big strategic mistake.} (6... cxd4 $1 7. Nxd4 Bxg2 8. Kxg2 a6 $132 9. e4 Be7
10. Qf3 Ra7 11. Nd2 O-O 12. Rfe1 h6 13. Be3 Rc7 14. c3 Nc6 15. Nxc6 Rxc6) (6...
Be7 $1 $132 7. dxc5 Bxc5 $1 (7... Na6 8. a4 b4) 8. Qd3 (8. a4 b4) 8... a6 9.
Nbd2 Be7 10. e4 d5 $132 (10... h6 11. Bxf6 Bxf6 12. e5 Be7 13. c3 Qc7)) 7. e4
$3 $16 Bxe4 $2 8. Nc3 Bb7 (8... Bc6 9. d5 $18) 9. d5 $18 {White gets
tremendous compensation for the sacrificed pawn - Black is unable to complete
his development.} *

